text.data-name: How To Apply For Student Visa?
Student Visas are provided to individuals who wish to come to I

svg.text: Student Visas are provided to individuals who wish to come to India and study at a recognized university. The entire process of student visa application only requires three steps: -

text.data-name: Individuals are first required to fill an online application fo

svg.text: Individuals are first required to fill an online application form by visiting the official website of Government of India i.e., https://indianvisaonline.gov.inAfter filling up the application form applicants are required to submit the same with all the required documents at the Indian Visa Application Center or at the Indian Mission.After successful document verification the passport and the student visa are generated which the applicant can retrieve from the Visa Application Center or the Indian Mission.
